From working/stay at home life and pumping to having multiple kids and busy lives, you’re all super parents. Here’s a day in the life.

⭐ Life with Nanobébé makes parenting a little bit more convenient
🎥 @malgalcinemas 
.
.
.

We’re giving away 6 Cookies & Cream 2-packs of our Flexy Silicone Bottles (3 on Instagram, 3 on Facebook)! Both of these exclusive colors are NOT available in stores or online!⁠
⁠
3 easy steps to enter:⁠
♡ Follow us @nanobebe_world⁠
♡ Like this post⁠
♡ Comment below with why you love Nanobébé products! 👇⁠

Giveaway closes Monday 7/19 at 11:59 pm PST, winners announced Tuesday, 7/20 on this post.⁠ Giveaway not affiliated with Instagram. Must be over 18 to enter. Open to US and Canada.⁠

DISCLAIMER: We DO NOT create separate giveaway accounts for contacting winners, nor do we EVER ask giveaway winners for payment information for any reason ever.
